name: Plucked Yamabuki Splendor
description: Chiori's outfit. An elegant dress ensemble personally designed by Chiori herself, the exquisite craftsmanship has a distinctive Inazuman flair. She once wore this outfit when she graced the front page of a Fontainian fashion review magazine, and her unique aesthetics immediately catapulted her to the forefront of Fontaine's fashion world.
